ocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 06, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104clg1665702749160.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/clg1665702749160.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/clg1665702749160.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"clg1665702749160\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Network On-Premises Served\n      License </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"clg1665702749160__on_premises_served_network_license_203355\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A network on-premise served license is a local license file (or license code) that\n      enables a Sentinel RMS License Manager (also called an RMS Server) to run concurrent licenses.\n      Applications connect to the RMS License Manager over the network. No internet connection is\n      required. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"clg1665702749160__p_d67172e1_d67173e1_d67174e1\">For more information about the license server, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"paz1665702747377.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/paz1665702747377.html\">Sentinel RMS License Manager</a>.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"clg1665702749160__li_d29825e1_d29826e1_d29827e1\">To configure a network on-premises served license,\n            see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mwx1665702749228.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwx1665702749228.html\" title=\"You are given an Entitlement ID when you register with Uniface, which allows you to access the Sentinel EMS customer portal, where you can lock your license to a specific machine and obtain the actual license file.\">Configuring Network On-Premises Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"clg1665702749160__li_d29828e1_d29829e1_d29830e1\">To return a network on-premises served license, see\n               <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qzo1665702749304.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qzo1665702749304.html\" title=\"If you need to return a network on-premises served license that is no longer required, use the Revocation tool, located in the /common/bin directory of your Uniface installation, as well as in the RMS installation package. This is a Java-based tool that can be run on any platform.\">Returning Network On-Premises Served Licenses</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526500\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Network On-Premises Served License Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 06, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Network On-Premises Served License A network on-premise served license is a local license file (or license code) that enables a Sentinel RMS License Manager (also called an RMS Server) to run concurrent licenses. Applications connect to the RMS License Manager over the network. No internet connection is required. For more information about the license server, see Sentinel RMS License Manager . To configure a network on-premises served license, see Configuring Network On-Premises Served Licenses . To return a network on-premises served license, see Returning Network On-Premises Served Licenses . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}